Problem statement
Add the functionality of deleting the expenses from the firebase using the deleteDocs() method.

When the delete button is clicked on an expense use the appropriate firebase method to delete the expense from the database.

Note:
This is a follow-up question to the previous expense tracker project use the same firebase configuration in the solution code.
You only need to change the deleteExpense() function in the App component.
